author: John Eliot
message: All the great performers I have worked with are fuelled by a personal dream.
title: Thought of the day

author: A. A. Milne
message: One of the advantages of being disorderly is that one is constantly making exciting discoveries.
title: Thought of the day

author: Marie Curie
message: I never see what has been done; I only see what remains to be done.
title: Thought of the day

author: Seneca
message: Begin at once to live and count each separate day as a separate life.
title: Thought of the day
